OL,3,CDame Jenni Murray, former BBC
OL,4,Cpresenter, dies aged 75
OL,6,FTalent management firm Knight Ayton
OL,7,Fcalled her "a true professional and
OL,8,Fpioneer" who "interviewed every prime
OL,9,Fminister of the last 30 years".
OL,11,FThey added: "She was as comfortable
OL,12,Fwith high-powered politicians as with
OL,13,Fthe grieving parents of Madeleine
OL,14,FMcCann, and the first Hollywood star
OL,15,Fshe encountered was Bette Davis."
OL,17,FShe was made a dame in 2011 in
OL,18,Frecognition of her contribution to
OL,19,Fbroadcasting and was awarded an OBE in
OL,20,F1999.
