OL,3,CDame Jenni Murray, former BBC
OL,4,Cpresenter, dies aged 75
OL,6,FDuring her tenure on Woman's Hour,
OL,7,FDame Jenni interviewed high-profile
OL,8,Ffigures such as Margaret Thatcher,
OL,9,FBarbara Castle, Shirley Williams,
OL,10,FGloria Steinem, Bette Davis, Monica
OL,11,FLewinsky and Hillary Clinton.
OL,13,FShe signed off her final episode of
OL,14,FWoman's Hour in October 2020 with
OL,15,FHelen Reddy's feminist anthem I Am
OL,16,FWoman.
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
